response.overview: After 20 incredible years of touring and making music together, we have decided to disband and make way for a new incarnation of The Cat Empire to come to life fronted by Felix and Ollie.  We are making sure everyone who can not attend a live performance this Australian Summer can join us for the final show of the original line-up via a virtual concert.  We have so much to celebrate and canâ€™t wait to have you dancing along with us from your lounge room or backyard.  The party will get started with a special piano solo set from our very own Ollie McGill before we move into two hours of The Cat Empire.  We have a set-list jam-packed with favourite songs from our entire career. Expect an unforgettable celebration with plenty of reflection and immeasurable joy.
response.title: The Cat Empire: Virtual Concert
